metadata.name: The Gravees #1
metadata.description: Gravees is anim8dead's genesis 1/1 art collection of 444 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain. Created using artificial intelligence in concert with a traditional art's background, they are a reflection on a career spent animating death. Inspired by your Gravee and have a story about it's life/personality? This collaborative art project wants YOUR creative description for the Gravees you minted, and I will add it here for future Purple Cloaks to witness.
